statements: SELECT * FROM vehicle_warranty;
SELECT vehicle_make, vehicle_model, expiration_date FROM vehicle_warranty WHERE warranty_provider = 'ABC Warranty';
SELECT id, warranty_provider, expiration_date FROM vehicle_warranty WHERE vehicle_make = 'Toyota' AND vehicle_model = 'Camry';
SELECT id, vehicle_make, vehicle_model, expiration_date FROM vehicle_warranty WHERE expiration_date >= '2023-01-01';
SELECT DISTINCT vehicle_make FROM vehicle_warranty;
SELECT * FROM vehicle_warranty WHERE warranty_provider = 'Manufacturer' ORDER BY expiration_date DESC;
SELECT vehicle_make, vehicle_model, expiration_date FROM vehicle_warranty WHERE warranty_coverage LIKE '%limited%' ORDER BY vehicle_make ASC, expiration_date ASC;
SELECT COUNT(*) AS warranty_count, warranty_provider FROM vehicle_warranty GROUP BY warranty_provider;
SELECT DISTINCT vehicle_make FROM vehicle_warranty WHERE expiration_date > '2022-01-01';
SELECT warranty_provider, COUNT(*) AS warranty_count FROM vehicle_warranty WHERE warranty_coverage IS NOT NULL GROUP BY warranty_provider HAVING COUNT(*) > 1;
SELECT * FROM vehicles;
SELECT make, model, year FROM vehicles WHERE year > 2010;
SELECT make, model FROM vehicles WHERE make = 'Toyota';
SELECT * FROM warranties WHERE expiration_date >= CURRENT_DATE;
SELECT vehicle_id, make, model, year FROM vehicles ORDER BY year DESC;
SELECT * FROM vehicles WHERE year > 2015 ORDER BY make ASC, model DESC;
SELECT make, model FROM vehicles WHERE make LIKE 'Toy%' AND year < 2020;
SELECT make, year FROM vehicles WHERE make = 'Honda' AND model = 'Civic' ORDER BY year DESC;
SELECT * FROM warranties LEFT JOIN vehicles ON warranties.vehicle_id = vehicles.vehicle_id WHERE expiration_date > '2022-01-01' ORDER BY expiration_date ASC;
SELECT make, model, YEAR(expiration_date) AS warranty_year FROM vehicles JOIN warranties ON vehicles.vehicle_id = warranties.vehicle_id WHERE make = 'Ford';
SELECT * FROM vehicles;
SELECT make, model, year FROM vehicles WHERE year < 2020;
SELECT coverage_id, coverage_type, coverage_description FROM warranty_coverage ORDER BY coverage_type DESC;
SELECT make, model, year, expiration_date FROM vehicles WHERE year >= 2018 ORDER BY expiration_date ASC;
SELECT vehicle_id, status FROM warranty_expiration WHERE status = 'Active';
SELECT make, model, year FROM vehicles WHERE year > 2010 ORDER BY make ASC, year DESC, model DESC LIMIT 5;

SELECT make, model, year, expiration_date FROM vehicles INNER JOIN warranty_expiration ON vehicles.vehicle_id = warranty_expiration.vehicle_id WHERE expiration_date < '2022-01-01' ORDER BY expiration_date ASC, make DESC LIMIT 5;

SELECT make, model, year, coverage_type, coverage_description FROM vehicles INNER JOIN warranty_coverage ON vehicles.vehicle_id = warranty_coverage.vehicle_id WHERE year = 2015 AND coverage_type = 'Extended' ORDER BY make ASC, model DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT make, model, coverage_details, expiration_date FROM vehicles WHERE make LIKE 'To%' ORDER BY coverage_details DESC, expiration_date ASC, make LIMIT 5;

SELECT vehicle_id, make, model, status FROM vehicles INNER JOIN warranty_expiration ON vehicles.vehicle_id = warranty_expiration.vehicle_id WHERE status = 'Active' ORDER BY make DESC, model ASC LIMIT 5;
SELECT * FROM Vehicles;
SELECT make, model, year FROM Vehicles WHERE year > 2010;
SELECT vehicle_id, make, warranty_provider FROM Vehicles WHERE make = 'Toyota';
SELECT * FROM WarrantyCoverage WHERE coverage_length > 2;
SELECT provider_name, contact_phone FROM WarrantyProviders ORDER BY provider_name DESC;
SELECT * FROM Vehicles;
SELECT make, model, year FROM Vehicles ORDER BY year DESC;
SELECT make, warranty_provider, warranty_expiration_date FROM Vehicles WHERE year > 2015;
SELECT v.make, wp.provider_name, wc.coverage_details FROM Vehicles v JOIN WarrantyProviders wp ON v.vehicle_id = wp.provider_id JOIN WarrantyCoverage wc ON v.vehicle_id = wc.coverage_id;
SELECT v.make, v.model, wp.contact_email FROM Vehicles v LEFT JOIN WarrantyProviders wp ON v.provider_id = wp.provider_id;
SELECT * FROM Vehicles;
SELECT make, model, year FROM Vehicles WHERE year > 2010;
SELECT vehicle_id, model, make, year FROM Vehicles ORDER BY year DESC;
SELECT * FROM WarrantyClaims WHERE claim_amount > 1000;
SELECT user_name, user_email FROM Users WHERE user_name LIKE '%John%';
SELECT * FROM Vehicles ORDER BY year DESC, make;
SELECT make, model, count(*) FROM Vehicles GROUP BY make, model;
SELECT Users.user_name, Vehicles.make, Vehicles.model FROM Users INNER JOIN Vehicles ON Users.user_id = Vehicles.vehicle_id;
SELECT vehicle_id, make, model, year FROM Vehicles WHERE year BETWEEN 2010 AND 2020 ORDER BY year;
SELECT warranty_id, coverage_details FROM WarrantyDetails WHERE expiration_date > '2022-01-01';
